metal,  slowcore,  ambient, electronic, or shoegazer.
It's  hard  to  mention my 10 favourite music groups.
But  let's  try: The Cure, Slowdive, This Empty Flow,
Clan  Of Xymox, Porcupine Tree, Anathema, Antimatter,
Legendary  Pink  Dots,  Dead Can Dance, Pink Floyd...

×008B:   Surrealistic   or   Realistic?×

S:  Surrealistic, copying the nature is boring to me,
I  don't  like  it. Instead, I feel a huge respect to
artists  who do it in a good way. Anyway, I've always
prefered to paint dreams, nightmares, fears and other
things  that  you  can  find  inside  of your head...

